                                                                                                      Intrusion Detection System.

                                                                                               As depicted in Figure 1, Skill statements describe what the learner can do, and Task statements
                                                                                               describe the work to be done. Therefore, it is important to separate the language used between
                                                                                               Skill statements and Task statements and to use terms that facilitate observability and assessment
                                                                                               of the learner.


